  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>... that <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> was not the first House of <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrian</a> origin to come to <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>? <a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\">House Velaryon</a> settled on the island of <a href=\"/index.php/Driftmark\" title=\"Driftmark\">Driftmark</a> before <a href=\"/index.php/Aenar_Targaryen\" title=\"Aenar Targaryen\">Aenar Targaryen</a> moved to <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonstone\" title=\"Dragonstone\">Dragonstone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf44.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf44.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Did_you_know/125&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf44.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf44.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings&#58; Jaehaerys I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403135556\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 98/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8552/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 428/2097152 